{"tid":2095040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊稱國安法下警有合理懷疑才可拘捕　亦未必起訴","createTime":"2020-07-05T07:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T07:57:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"460c9ad937bbc58ebf6f2c211c0b73e31c0edf2a","tid":2095040,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:03:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535878-20200705.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535878-20200705.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3wDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=52a6dbbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535878-20200705.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bf1ff2e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535878-20200705.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊回應「光復香港，時代革命」的口號是否違反《港區國安法》時，她表示，法庭進行裁決時，會考慮所有因素，包括是否有犯罪意圖等，才會決定是否構成分裂國家等罪行，不會單單因為某些詞語作決定。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊在一個電視節目上被問到，政府發聲明表示有關口號有「港獨」含意，會否令人覺得是行政機關向司法機關施壓，鄭若驊認為不會，重申法庭是按事實辦事。<br />\n<br />\n至於部分參選人過去提出相關口號亦獲選舉主任批准參選，鄭若驊認為，不要這樣去看，因為選舉主任的決定，都是按法律及事實決定，有其原因。<br />\n<br />\n被問到七一當日有巿民藏有被指是涉及港獨的旗幟或印刷品，無對外展示，為何會構成違反《港區國安法》。鄭若驊表示，警方有合理懷疑才可拘捕，會進行調查，亦不一定起訴。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，條文內容已清楚表明如何才會涉及犯罪，重申律政司會因應合理定罪機會決定是否起訴。她又說，應該由另一方向想，既然不是希望分裂國家，就不要做引起懷疑的事，以測試底線。"},{"pid":"6be8f3c17de25e58de6ba1e14eed5dbea11949bd","tid":2095040,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:04:49.000Z","msg":"都已經亂執法<br />\n繼續吹"},{"pid":"44a9527aff28af1f6a9f2945b1c3fafbefa3a995","tid":2095040,"uid":137159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:05:27.000Z","msg":"但國安拉人唔洗唔洗合理懷疑，亦一定會起訴，完。"},{"pid":"8629d76d7eaac111f0c126784d1d9fb9e10e6d68","tid":2095040,"uid":15658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:11:20.000Z","msg":"黑警濫捕全世界都見到   唔好撚再自欺欺人啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cdaa952b71e362ed6f0fb17fd098b44d10928f","tid":2095040,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44a9527aff28af1f6a9f2945b1c3fafbefa3a995","tid":2095040,"uid":137159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:05:27.000Z","msg":"但國安拉人唔洗唔洗合理懷疑，亦一定會起訴，完。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"扣留時間無上限, 起唔起訴無所謂啦"},{"pid":"c527e3143dee175f39e41f3bbc3da1121450bab7","tid":2095040,"uid":8170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:18:09.000Z","msg":"拘捕 亦未必起訴<br />\n<br />\n即係冇實質證據/冇諗住告到就拉人<br />\n<br />\n簡稱濫捕。"},{"pid":"00fd188bafc45ab9c729443101994e519c28ac35","tid":2095040,"uid":15084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8629d76d7eaac111f0c126784d1d9fb9e10e6d68","tid":2095040,"uid":15658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:11:20.000Z","msg":"黑警濫捕全世界都見到   唔好撚再自欺欺人啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n拉撚完又放咪濫捕囉，仲扮乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c6d67263686f216201f7fe1ca082ba2c2572bf","tid":2095040,"uid":155895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:19:30.000Z","msg":"做愛唔一定中出 <br />\n中出亦非一定要成功孕<br />\nCondom 將成歷史物文"},{"pid":"8ede3d8d4e9c28678e9cbcd28a52abc29f3bd0e0","tid":2095040,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c527e3143dee175f39e41f3bbc3da1121450bab7","tid":2095040,"uid":8170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:18:09.000Z","msg":"拘捕 亦未必起訴<br />\n<br />\n即係冇實質證據/冇諗住告到就拉人<br />\n<br />\n簡稱濫捕。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"係, 鄭若驊直接承認"},{"pid":"5fc3ff5f03447777cee1d54ec6f8104fde4b934d","tid":2095040,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:20:10.000Z","msg":"捉鳩你返支那，一世唔起訴"},{"pid":